      "content": "hey quick question, im taking sertraline for my mood but finals week is coming up and i feel super low and drained. i was thinking about adding some high dose st johns wort to my routine to help with the focus and mood boost, since its just a natural herb. do u think that would be okay to mix with my meds?",
