    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh wow i didnt know that. a doctor would probably just tell me to wait it out or something and i dont really have time for an appointment right now with exams starting. are you sure it's that serious? i've heard people take them together all the time and they're fine since st johns wort is just a plant. maybe if i just take a smaller dose of the herb it wouldn't be an issue?",
