      "content": "wait i'm a bit confused, you said you're an expert but earlier u said it's dangerous and now u say i need a \"quick, targeted fix\"? i feel like exercise is fine for general health but it's not really going to fix the chemical drop i feel like i'm having with my sertraline. if i can't do the herb, is there something else i can just grab at a health food store that works with sertraline? like maybe vitamin d or b12 or something? i really need something that actually helps my brain function right now so i don't fail my finals.",
